            <br><br>
            You can find her work almost everywhere. Whether it&apos;s thumbing through pages of spreads in trendy hair magazines, or ad campaigns by your favorite hair product lines, Evie&apos;s work speaks for itself. She has also personally styled celebrity notables and industry recording artist clients such as Tasha Smith, Trey Songz, Laurie Ann Gibson, Chrisette Michelle, Debra L. Lee, and Deborah Cox just to name a few.
            <br><br>
            Although Evie runs a tight schedule at her salon with her favorite, every day clients, she makes time to share and educate her fellow beauty professionals with her cutting edge styling techniques as well as her latest hair shaping trends and custom hair units. Using skills she&apos;s acquired over the years, Evie educates beauty professionals on taking their careers to levels some thought they could only imagine achieving. Whether it be photo shoots, film, everyday women, or wanting to be the star of your next event Evie is the stylist for you and for the beauty industry professional wanting to take their career to that next level Evie is the educator for you.
          </div>
        </div>

